    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3352560/extras/996aabc0eb8d4cf8b53c8885b48b78e6.avif?t=1764866831\" width=630 height=110 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>&quot;In the lonely wasteland that leads to a mining site, someone dumps the body of a woman and a series of horrible clues with the cryptic message of her killer at night. Who is hiding to commit such atrocities and why? Nicolas, the young owner of Bar Delirio, has decided to discover the murderer to protect the life of the only family he has left: his little niece. But he won't be alone. If he trust the right person, he might find more than just the truth. Maybe he will end up discovering his true desires in the Delirium.&quot;</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Romance and thriller Visual Novel in English and Spanish.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3352560/extras/dcf49f46632bddd9347f0051a314acfb.avif?t=1764866831\" width=630 height=110 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crafting recipes for Bar Delirio.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore Aguasvivas Town with map events.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect mysteries and solve the case.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose between 5 unique characters' romantic routes. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple Endings based on your choices.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3352560/extras/c5cb08d28fdc6654cdcc2a1244fc7c21.avif?t=1764866831\" width=630 height=110 /></span><i>Night in Delirium is being developed with Ren'Py. A demo is currently available, which includes a tutorial and the first two chapters of the story.</i></p>",
    "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3352560/extras/996aabc0eb8d4cf8b53c8885b48b78e6.avif?t=1764866831\" width=630 height=110 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>&quot;In the lonely wasteland that leads to a mining site, someone dumps the body of a woman and a series of horrible clues with the cryptic message of her killer at night. Who is hiding to commit such atrocities and why? Nicolas, the young owner of Bar Delirio, has decided to discover the murderer to protect the life of the only family he has left: his little niece. But he won't be alone. If he trust the right person, he might find more than just the truth. Maybe he will end up discovering his true desires in the Delirium.&quot;</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Romance and thriller Visual Novel in English and Spanish.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3352560/extras/dcf49f46632bddd9347f0051a314acfb.avif?t=1764866831\" width=630 height=110 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crafting recipes for Bar Delirio.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore Aguasvivas Town with map events.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect mysteries and solve the case.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose between 5 unique characters' romantic routes. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple Endings based on your choices.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3352560/extras/c5cb08d28fdc6654cdcc2a1244fc7c21.avif?t=1764866831\" width=630 height=110 /></span><i>Night in Delirium is being developed with Ren'Py. A demo is currently available, which includes a tutorial and the first two chapters of the story.</i></p>",
    "short_description": "A series of murders puts a town in Chile on alert, and the police are unable to identify the perpetrator and his strange messages. Meanwhile, Nicolas, the young owner of Bar Delirio, suspects that the culprit is hiding among his frequent customers.",
